{"tid":2224211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天台遺書包 蘇屋邨14歲中學生墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:07:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e40cb5c7f344c6533d52ef2db7a9d389234aad21","tid":2224211,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，警方接獲報案，指一名年約14歲的男童在長沙灣蘇屋邨金松樓的高處墮下，倒卧平台位置，昏迷不醒，救援人員趕到現場，發現男童已經死亡，警員其後聯絡上男童的家人，其母親亦在天台發現男童的書包，正調查男童墮樓的原因。現場消息指，男童今日需要上學，事發前曾與家人發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200930/SDWAK2AXXVAUDFDVHBLLJNCG7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200930%2FSDWAK2AXXVAUDFDVHBLLJNCG7I%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=15028260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200930%2FSDWAK2AXXVAUDFDVHBLLJNCG7I%2F&h=71090023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200930/SDWAK2AXXVAUDFDVHBLLJNCG7I/</a>"},{"pid":"6b0dad097a10700f302f1784b6fca6b77feb3360","tid":2224211,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a933af74c10b6d8d9158a72d10b3b8a49f01e323","tid":2224211,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b0dad097a10700f302f1784b6fca6b77feb3360","tid":2224211,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\